from AI replacing-- I mean,

00:34:19.440 --> 00:34:23.484
I heard the other day that you
guys, with that Google-- that

00:34:23.484 --> 00:34:27.590
Go program, you did something
that no one thought would

00:34:27.590 --> 00:34:31.060
