the way music affects us.

00:35:06.620 --> 00:35:07.980
It's a commonality.

00:35:07.980 --> 00:35:10.060
It's deep in our
emotional system.

00:35:10.060 --> 00:35:12.780
It tells us that we're
really all the same.

00:35:12.780 --> 00:35:14.410
It's very emotional.

00:35:14.410 --> 00:35:18.400
